title: #66 - YouTube Is Doomed, 30 Year Old Mall Ninja Evicted & Kendrick Lamar
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast Hila is out of town so instead Erik is here as a substitute carer for Ethan. Together they discuss the future of YouTube, the fate of the 30 year old mall ninja evictee, the recent school shooting incidents, and Kendrick Lamar's ill advised choice to bring a white fan up on stage to perform one of his tracks!
itunes:author: Ethan Klein
